OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FLabour MPs are among a group of more
OL,7,Fthan 60 parliamentarians to have made
OL,8,Fpublic their opposition to the planned
OL,9,FRosebank oil field ` with one of Sir
OL,10,FKeir Starmer's backbenchers urging the
OL,11,FGovernment to rule against the
OL,12,Fdevelopment and take a stand "against
OL,13,FTrump, Reform and their fossil fuel
OL,14,Fpaymasters".
OL,26,@tD@^OUvD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
