CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772422502
OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FClive Lewis is one of more than 50 MPs
OL,7,Fat Westminster who have signed a
OL,8,Fpledge from campaign group Uplift to
OL,9,F"oppose the Rosebank oil field" and
OL,10,Finstead "advocate for a properly
OL,11,Ffunded just transition for oil and gas
OL,12,Fworkers and communities".
OL,14,FUrging the Government to reject the
OL,15,Fdevelopment, Norwich South MP Mr Lewis
OL,16,Fsaid: "We must stand our ground
OL,17,Fagainst Trump, Reform and their fossil
OL,18,Ffuel paymasters.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@_O]rD@IOUtD@XO]xD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772422502
OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,F"Approving an enormous new oil field
OL,7,Fwould mean caving in to their anti-
OL,8,Fclimate, anti-renewables agenda that
OL,9,Fruns completely counter to our values
OL,10,Fand our long-term interests."
OL,12,FScottish Labour MP Chris Murray,
OL,13,Fanother of the Labour MPs to have
OL,14,Fsigned the pledge, said the decision
OL,15,Fon Rosebank was "an opportunity for
OL,16,Fthe Government to change course".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@]O]wD@QOUxD@`O]
