CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772422502
OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FThe group includes Mr Lewis, Mr
OL,7,FMurray, former Labour shadow
OL,8,Fchancellor John McDonnell and Scottish
OL,9,FLabour's Brian Leishman.
OL,11,FFormer Labour MPs Jeremy Corbyn and
OL,12,FDiane Abbott have also signed the
OL,13,Fpledge, along with a number of Liberal
OL,14,FDemocrat and Green MPs, SNP MP Chris
OL,15,FLaw, Plaid Cymru's Liz Saville Roberts
OL,16,Fand Paul Maskey of Sinn Fein.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
