OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FIn Scotland a number of Labour MSPs
OL,7,Fhave signed the pledge, along with
OL,8,FGreen MSPs ` including the party's
OL,9,FScottish co-leader Ross Greer ` and
OL,10,Fformer SNP health secretary Michael
OL,11,FMatheson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
