OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772422503
OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FWhile previous Scottish first
OL,7,Fministers Nicola Sturgeon and Humza
OL,8,FYousaf made plain their opposition to
OL,9,FRosebank, First Minister John Swinney
OL,10,Fhas insisted the Scottish Government
OL,11,Ftakes a "case-by-case approach" to new
OL,12,Foil and gas developments, stressing
OL,13,Fthese should only proceed if found to
OL,14,Fbe compatible with climate change
OL,15,Ftargets.
OL,17,FMr Lewis said opposing Rosebank would
OL,18,F"show that a Labour Government will
OL,19,Fstand by the promises we made to the
OL,20,Fcountry".
