OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772422503
OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FHe added: "There are only so many
OL,7,Ftimes we can afford to make mistakes
OL,8,Fand then change course.
OL,10,F"With Rosebank, we have an opportunity
OL,11,Fto get it right the first time."
OL,13,FMr Murray, the Labour MP for Edinburgh
OL,14,FEast and Musselburgh, said many locals
OL,15,Fin his constituency were "deeply
OL,16,Fconcerned about Rosebank and rightly
OL,17,Fso".
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUsD@`O]wD@ZOUyD@CO]
