OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1772422503
OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FHe added: "Climate change is one of
OL,7,Fthe reasons I came into politics, and
OL,8,Fopening new oil and gas fields is
OL,9,Fsimply incompatible with our climate
OL,10,Fcommitments.
OL,12,F"With the North Sea's oil supply
OL,13,Fdwindling, Scotland's energy sector
OL,14,Fmust transition to clean energy, or
OL,15,Fworkers risk being left behind."
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUwD@`O]
