OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FScottish Labour MSP Mercedes Villalba,
OL,7,Fwho has also signed the pledge, argued
OL,8,Fthat "approving projects like Rosebank
OL,9,Fwill lock us into a toxic dependence
OL,10,Fon volatile, conflict-ridden fossil
OL,11,Ffuels".
OL,13,FThis would create "another excuse to
OL,14,Fdelay the urgent investment needed to
OL,15,Fcreate secure, well-paid jobs for
OL,16,FScotland's workers", she added.
OL,26,@pD@FOUsD@FO]uD@SOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
