OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FMs Villalba said: "In an increasingly
OL,7,Funcertain world, where climate action
OL,8,Fis relegated in favour of fossil
OL,9,Fpolitics, the UK and Scotland must
OL,10,Flead the way on the clean energy
OL,11,Ftransition."
OL,13,FWera Hobhouse, Liberal Democrat MP for
OL,14,FBath, said people in her constituency
OL,15,Fand across the country "are already
OL,16,Ffacing the consequences of an
OL,17,Fincreasingly unstable climate".
OL,26,@nD@SOUsD@LO]wD@XOUyD@^O]
