OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FHighlighting the impact of flooding
OL,7,Fand "skyrocketing food prices", she
OL,8,Fsaid that "climate impacts are now a
OL,9,Fdaily reality".
OL,11,FMs Hobhouse said: "Extreme weather is
OL,12,Fdamaging crops, putting pressure on
OL,13,Ffarmers, and destroying our precious
OL,14,Fnatural environment.
OL,16,F"We cannot ignore these warning signs.
OL,18,F"A massive new oil field like Rosebank
OL,19,Fwould only make matters worse.
