OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,F"The emissions would be enormous,
OL,7,Flocking us into decades more pollution
OL,8,Fwhen we should be cutting carbon and
OL,9,Funlocking the benefits of cheap,
OL,10,Frenewable energy."
OL,12,FApproving the Rosebank development
OL,13,Fwould "make a mockery of Labour's
OL,14,Fenvironmental promises", she said.
