OL,3,CLabour parliamentarians urge UK
OL,4,CGovernment to oppose Rosebank oil field
OL,6,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our priority is to deliver a fair,
OL,8,Forderly and prosperous transition in
OL,9,Fthe North Sea in line with our climate
OL,10,Fand legal obligations, which drives
OL,11,Four clean energy future of energy
OL,12,Fsecurity, lower bills, and good long-
OL,13,Fterm jobs."
